amaser host galaxy NGC4258. From a\nmegamaser-TRGB-SBF distance ladder we obtain $D=18.7 \\pm 1.7$ Mpc, consistent\nwith our previous measurement and with the distance to the elliptical galaxy\nNGC1052.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Jul 2018 18:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Aug 2018 21:42:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
